      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 7,
      "message": "The commit is not handling YAML errors, so I don't think the summary makes sense. And, if you were following the guidelines, you would not start the summary with \"Service\", but with an imperative verb, e.g.:\nHandle CSAR reading errors in Service Import",
