      "file_path": "catalog-ui/src/app/view-models/workspace/tabs/general/general-view-model.ts",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 308,
      "message": "This code is reading a zip file, and files inside the zip. You can have problems not related to syntax, for example, if you provide a corrupted zip file, a file that has a zip extension but it is not a zip in content and so on.\nSo you can't generalize the error given here as syntax, what you can say is that there was an error reading the CSAR.",
